::: MEGATRON drifted away from Inferno and sailed into a clear area. He took 
out his comm ::: Oh would you all stop fighting! I put shredder in charge 
because you were injured and lost. You two will have to put up with each 
other right now! I suppose I will come to your posit-

::: His comm broke off and a chuckle came from the shadows :::

::: TRANSANULAS ::: So, Megatron, your still alive I see.

::: MEGATRON ::: Spider, what do you want?

::: TRANSANULAS ::: Im the one who called the Oblitercons to help 
Quickstrike. They will escort him here, meanwhile you will have already taken 
over the ship. While the Oblitercons and there new proto-form fight it out 
outside with the Predacons, we will take over the ship.

::: MEGATRON ::: What?!

::: TRANSANULAS ::: I think I will be giving the orders now, shorty!

::: He smacked Megatrons small body to the ground ::: 

::: TRANSANULAS ::: Now go to Quickstrike and get the codes, before i destroy 
you...or turn you over to Hell Beast.

::: Megatron growled, and with no choice fled to Quickstrikes position :::
